high_descs: advance forward slightly, and then stop and turn right in front of the toaster
take the spatula from the counter
turn around and go to the stove, then face the stove
place the spatula in the pot on the back right burner of the stove
take the pot containing the spatula
turn left, and cross the room to the door. Turn right to face the rectangular table when you arrive at the door
place the pot on the right-hand, back side of the table
anns.task_desc: Place a pot containing a spatula on the rectangular table

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the green trash can.
Pick up the spatula to the left of the toaster on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the stove.
Place the spatula in the pot on the right of the stove.
Pick up the pot with a spatula in it.
Turn left and walk to the table next to the door.
Place the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a spatula in it on the table next to the door.

high_descs: Go to the end of the counter.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Put the spatula in the wok on the front of the stove.
Pick up the wok on the front of the stove.
Turn left and go to the table.
Put the wok on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the wok on the stove to the table.
